                                                                                                                                    conﬁguraon sengs and associated documentaon; list of failures requiring
                                                                                                                                    system to fail in a known state; state informaon to be preserved in system failure;
                                                                                                                                    system audit records; system security plan; other relevant documents or records].

                                                                                                              SC-24-Interview       [SELECT FROM: System/network administrators; organizaonal personnel with
                                                                                                                                    informaon security responsibilies; system developer].

